jalds.alds.ds.graphs
Class WeightedGraph

java.lang.Object
  jalds.alds.ds.graphs.WeightedGraph

public class WeightedGraph
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a graph where the edges have weights associated with them. This class delegates all work to the Graph class except for maintaining the weights of edges.

Author:
Devender Gollapally
